# Thread Review
- Lightweight process: basic unit of **CPU utilization**.
- Treads **belonging to the same process** share:
  - Code section.
  - Data section.
  - OS resources (open files, signals, etc.).
- Each thread has its own thread control block (TCB)
  - Thread ID.
  - Program counter.
  - Register set.
  - Stack.
